              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 2 anti-coincidence-shielded Nai(Tl)",
                " spectrometers locvated 80.6 cm from sample and",
                " surrounded by 10 cm of passive Pb shielding as well",
                " as 20 cm of lithium-carbonated paraffin to moderate",
                " neutrons.  Cadmium or boron shields in front of the",
                " detectors absorbed thermal neutrons.",
